
QUICK INSTALL
-------------

- you need a regular gcc compiler. Version 2.96 will do fine
- type "make" in this directory
- get a 1.4 MB DOS formatted floppy (FAT filesystem)
- copy the following files to the floppy:
    hermes/nucleus/kernel.img
    hermes/appl.os/boot/boot
    hermes/appl.os/window/window
    hermes/appl/user/tetris
    hermes/appl/user/user
    hermes/tools/loader/load.exe
- reboot the system in DOS mode
- connect a PS/2 mouse
- type "load kernel.img"

Voila!
